      "content": {
        "html": "<div id=\"root\"><div class=\"page\"><nav class=\"nav\"><div class=\"nav-inner\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"logo\">acme</a><div class=\"nav-links\"><a href=\"#features\" class=\"nav-link\">Features</a><a href=\"#pricing\" class=\"nav-link\">Pricing</a><a href=\"#about\" class=\"nav-link\">About</a><a href=\"#blog\" class=\"nav-link\">Blog</a></div><div class=\"nav-actions\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">Sign In</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\">Get Started</a></div></div></nav><section class=\"hero\"><span class=\"badge\">New: AI Insights now in Beta</span><h1 class=\"hero-title\">Build faster.<br>Scale smarter.</h1><p class=\"hero-subtitle\">The modern platform for teams that ship. APIs, analytics, and infrastructure — all in one place.</p><div class=\"hero-actions\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg\">Start Building — Free</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-ghost btn-lg\">View Documentation</a></div><div class=\"hero-visual\"><div class=\"code-window\"><div class=\"code-dots\"><span class=\"dot dot-red\"></span><span class=\"dot dot-yellow\"></span><span class=\"dot dot-green\"></span></div><pre class=\"code-body\">const acme = new Acme({ apiKey: \"ak_live_...\" });\n\nconst result = await acme.analyze({\n  dataset: \"events\",\n  metric: \"conversion_rate\",\n  window: \"7d\",\n});\n\nconsole.log(result.insights);\n// → [{ type: \"anomaly\", confidence: 0.97, ... }]</pre></div></div></section><section class=\"stats\" id=\"features\"><div class=\"stats-grid\"><div class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-value\">99.99%</span><span class=\"stat-label\">Uptime SLA</span></div><div class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-value\">12M+</span><span class=\"stat-label\">API Calls / Day</span></div><div class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-value\">3,200+</span><span class=\"stat-label\">Companies</span></div><div class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-value\">&lt;50ms</span><span class=\"stat-label\">Avg Latency</span></div></div></section><section class=\"features\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Everything you need to ship</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle\">One platform. No glue code. No vendor lock-in.</p><div class=\"features-grid\"><div class=\"feature-card\"><span class=\"feature-icon\">⚡</span><h3 class=\"feature-title\">Lightning Fast</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\">Sub-millisecond response times with our globally distributed edge network.</p></div><div class=\"feature-card\"><span class=\"feature-icon\">🔒</span><h3 class=\"feature-title\">Secure by Default</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\">End-to-end encryption, SOC 2 certified, and zero-trust architecture.</p></div><div class=\"feature-card\"><span class=\"feature-icon\">📊</span><h3 class=\"feature-title\">Real-time Analytics</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\">Monitor every metric with live dashboards and custom alerting rules.</p></div><div class=\"feature-card\"><span class=\"feature-icon\">🔌</span><h3 class=\"feature-title\">Plug &amp; Play APIs</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\">RESTful and GraphQL APIs with SDKs for every major language.</p></div><div class=\"feature-card\"><span class=\"feature-icon\">🤖</span><h3 class=\"feature-title\">AI-Powered Insights</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\">Machine learning models surface patterns you would never spot manually.</p></div><div class=\"feature-card\"><span class=\"feature-icon\">🌍</span><h3 class=\"feature-title\">Global Scale</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\">Deploy to 40+ regions with automatic failover and load balancing.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"testimonials\" id=\"about\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Loved by engineering teams</h2><div class=\"testimonials-grid\"><div class=\"testimonial-card\"><p class=\"testimonial-quote\">\"Acme cut our infrastructure costs by 40% while improving reliability. The migration was seamless.\"</p><div class=\"testimonial-author\"><div class=\"avatar\">SC</div><div><div class=\"author-name\">Sarah Chen</div><div class=\"author-role\">CTO, Streamline</div></div></div></div><div class=\"testimonial-card\"><p class=\"testimonial-quote\">\"The API design is the best I have worked with. Our team shipped the integration in a single sprint.\"</p><div class=\"testimonial-author\"><div class=\"avatar\">MR</div><div><div class=\"author-name\">Marcus Rivera</div><div class=\"author-role\">Lead Engineer, Nexus</div></div></div></div><div class=\"testimonial-card\"><p class=\"testimonial-quote\">\"We moved from three separate tools to just Acme. The analytics alone are worth it.\"</p><div class=\"testimonial-author\"><div class=\"avatar\">EK</div><div><div class=\"author-name\">Elena Kowalski</div><div class=\"author-role\">VP Eng, Orbital</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pricing\" id=\"pricing\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Simple, transparent pricing</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle\">No hidden fees. Cancel anytime.</p><div class=\"pricing-grid\"><div class=\"pricing-card \"><h3 class=\"pricing-name\">Starter</h3><div class=\"pricing-price\">$29<span class=\"pricing-period\">/mo</span></div><p class=\"pricing-desc\">For small teams getting started</p><ul class=\"pricing-features\"><li class=\"pricing-feature\"><span class=\"check\">✓</span> 5 team members</li><li class=\"pricing-feature\"><span class=\"check\">✓</span> 10K API calls/mo</li><li class=\"pricing-feature\"><span class=\"check\">✓</span> Basic analytics</li><li class=\"pricing-feature\"><span class=\"check\">✓</span> Email support</li></ul><a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-lg btn-full btn-outline\">Start Free Trial</a></div><div class=\"pricing-card pricing-card--highlighted\"><h3 class=\"pricing-name\">Pro</h3><div class=\"pricing-price\">$99<span class=\"pricing-period\">/mo</span></div><p class=\"pricing-desc\">For growing teams that need more</p><ul class=\"pricing-features\"><li class=\"pricing-feature\"><span class=\"check\">✓</span> 25 team members</li><li class=\"pricing-feature\"><span class=\"check\">✓</span> 500K API calls/mo</li><li class=\